Message in which OscarMeyr submitted eir proto-Budget for GWotO:
http://www.agoranomic.org/pipermail/agora-business/2003-September/001970.html

Message in which the end of the GWotO election was announced:
http://www.agoranomic.org/pipermail/agora-official/2003-September/000819.html

========================================================================

Judge Sir Toby's Arguments:

There was no voting period in the election, therefore Rule 1958, paragraph
(e) did not cause the budget to change.

